r employer, and the calculation of the percent of revenue expended on certificated staff salaries and benefits.</s></p><div style="margin:0 0 1em 0;"></div><s><p style="margin-left: 4em;">(iii)<span class="EnSpace"/>Documentation for instruction and related services
